				<div class="entry-content">
			<p class="wp-flattr-button"><a href="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/?flattrss_redirect&amp;id=4146&amp;md5=b21fe6a10dff7310c93dee5caeaea322" title="Flattr" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/wp-content/plugins/flattr/img/flattr-badge-large.png" alt="flattr this!"/></a></p><audio id="podlovewebplayer_1" style="width: auto; height: 30px" controls type="audio/mpeg" preload="none" src="http://www.podtrac.com/pts/redirect.mp3/media.tipsfromthetopfloor.com/tfttf588_japanwildlife.mp3" type="audio/mpeg" preload="none">
