<li><a href="http://tfttf.com/chrisinjapan" target="_blank">Chris&#8217; behind-the-scenes photos from Japan</a></li>
<li><a href="https://plus.google.com/events/c0vkl478d86pl3hb315ign89l9k?authkey=CMrYzpTHkZLMYg" target="_blank">Event page for the Winter Wonderland Tour</a></li>
<li><a href="http://oneminuteinthelifeof.chrismarquardt.com/" target="_blank">Chris&#8217;s One Minute In The Life Of Videos</a></li>
</ul>
